Description: Cubes of marinated paneer grilled to perfection. Chef Meera Singh, a master of Indian cuisine, skillfully prepares this flavorful vegetarian appetizer.
Tender chicken in a rich, buttery tomato gravy with a blend of Indian spices. Chef Priya Patel's expertise results in this delectable and savory delight.
Paneer cubes in a creamy spinach sauce with a medley of Indian spices. Chef Aarti Kapoor's culinary mastery is evident in this delightful vegetarian dish.
Creamy risotto with mushrooms, white wine, and Parmesan cheese. Chef Carlo Bianchi's Risotto ai Funghi is a savory and aromatic Italian delight.
Thinly sliced marinated beef grilled to perfection. Chef Sun-woo Lee's Bulgogi is a savory and tender Korean barbecue delight with a sweet and smoky flavor.
Tender marinated chicken skewers grilled to perfection. Chef Yasmine Khalil's Shish Taouk is a flavorful and aromatic Arabian delight.
